Notepad++ v8.9.4 crash fixes, bug-fixes & new improvements:

 1. Fix crashes in FindInFiles when nativeLang.xml's "find-result-hits" contains "%s".
 2. Fix drop-file crash when file path length reaches 259 characters.
 3. Fix crash caused by undoing column editor bad input in virtual space.
 4. Fix bad column editor input in reverse-direction column selection on virtual space.
 5. Update to Scintilla 5.6.1 & Lexilla 5.4.8.
 6. Fix EOL conversion to Windows format not working (Scintilla update related).
 7. Fix rendering corruption in .bat files (Lexilla update related).
 8. Fix quote escaping causing incorrect JSON syntax highlighting (Lexilla update related).
 9. Fix MSI installation error due to context menu item registration.
10. Fix NSIS installation stalling caused by context menu registration issue.
11. Add NPP_LANG property to install a specific localization file for MSI.
12. Fix MSI installer display random Hexadecimal number as name on UAC.
13. Add version info into MSI file property (as value of "Comments").
14. Fix minimized window not restoring in administrator mode.
15. Fix Unicode search mismatching ANSI character '?'.
16. Fix Column Editor regression with empty fields.
17. Fix floating dialog content not displaying in certain situations.
18. Fix visual glitch when toggling group view in Document List.
19. Support improved C++ 11 raw string literal handling.
20. Fix visual glitch in the Mark dialog.


Get more info on
https://notepad-plus-plus.org/downloads/v8.9.4/


Included plugins:

 1.  NppExport v0.4
 2.  Converter v4.7
 3.  Mime Tool v3.1


